  • java.lang.Object
    • Service
      • at.fhooe.mc.conconii.GpsService

  • public class GpsService
extends Service
    This is the service for receiving gps data which is sent to the DataManger This service runs in his own thread and listens for Location updates

      • isEnabled

        public boolean isEnabled()
        Is called to check whether the GPS-provider is enabled or not. Is called by the android.content.ServiceConnection callback. Additionally sends a broadcast for each result.
        Returns:
        True if enabled, false otherwise

      • requestUpdates
